        <li class="plan-feature">Odour elimination</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#contact" class="plan-btn plan-btn-outline">Book Full Detail</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── REVIEWS ── -->
<section id="reviews">
  <div class="center">
    <div class="section-label reveal">Customer Reviews</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">What Our Customers Say</h2>
    <p class="section-sub reveal">Don't take our word for it. Here's what real AquaShine customers have to say about their experience.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="reviews-grid">
    <div class="review-card reveal">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="review-text">I've tried every car wash in the area and nothing compares to AquaShine. My car came out looking better than the day I bought it. The detailing package is absolutely worth every penny.</p>
      <div class="review-author">
        <div class="author-av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2d8bde,#00c6ff)">MR</div>
        <div>
          <div class="author-name">Marcus Rivera</div>
          <div class="author-info">Full Detailing Package · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review-card reveal">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="review-text">Fast, friendly, and incredibly thorough. I booked the premium wash online, was in and out in 25 minutes, and my car looked absolutely spotless. Will be a regular customer for sure!</p>
      <div class="review-author">
        <div class="author-av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7b5ea7,#a78bd4)">SP</div>
        <div>
          <div class="author-name">Sophia Park</div>
          <div class="author-info">Premium Wash · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review-card reveal">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="review-text">The team at AquaShine are genuinely passionate about what they do. My SUV had years of embedded dirt and they made it look brand new. Eco-friendly products are a huge bonus too.</p>
      <div class="review-author">
        <div class="author-av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#059669,#34d399)">JT</div>
        <div>
          <div class="author-name">James Thompson</div>
          <div class="author-info">Wax & Polish · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review-card reveal">
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="review-text">Best value car wash I've ever found. The staff are professional and clearly trained well. I've been coming here every two weeks for six months and the quality is consistently excellent.</p>
      <div class="review-author">
        <div class="author-av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f5a623,#fbbf24)">AL</div>
        <div>
          <div class="author-name">Aisha Lewis</div>
          <div class="author-info">Basic Wash (Regular) · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── CONTACT ── -->
<section id="contact">
  <div class="contact-grid">
    <div class="contact-info">
      <div class="section-label reveal">Location & Contact</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Come Visit Us or <span>Get in Touch</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">We're conveniently located and easy to reach. Book online, call us, or just stop by — we're always ready to make your car shine.</p>

      <div class="contact-detail reveal">
        <div class="contact-icon">📍</div>
        <div class="contact-text">
          <h4>Our Location</h4>
          <p>123 Shine Boulevard, Auto District<br>Los Angeles, CA 90001</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-detail reveal">
        <div class="contact-icon">📞</div>
        <div class="contact-text">
          <h4>Phone Number</h4>
          <p>(555) 123-4567</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-detail reveal">
        <div class="contact-icon">✉️</div>
        <div class="contact-text">
          <h4>Email Address</h4>
          <p>hello@aquashine.com</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-detail reveal">
        <div class="contact-icon">🕐</div>
        <div class="contact-text">
          <h4>Opening Hours</h4>
          <p>Mon–Fri: 7am–7pm &nbsp;|&nbsp; Sat–Sun: 8am–6pm</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="map-placeholder reveal">
        <!-- Replace with actual Google Maps embed URL -->
        <iframe
          src="https://www.openstreetmap.org/export/embed.html?bbox=-118.27%2C33.99%2C-118.22%2C34.03&layer=mapnik"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
          title="AquaShine Car Wash Location">
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-form reveal">
      <h3>📅 Book Your Wash</h3>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>First Name</label>
          <input type="text" placeholder="John"/>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Last Name</label>
          <input type="text" placeholder="Smith"/>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Phone / Email</label>
        <input type="text" placeholder="(555) 000-0000 or email@example.com"/>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Service Required</label>
        <select>
          <option>Basic Exterior Wash — $15</option>
          <option>Interior Cleaning — $25</option>
          <option>Premium Wash — $45</option>
          <option>Wax & Polish — $45</option>
          <option>Full Car Detailing — $120</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Preferred Date</label>
          <input type="date"/>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Preferred Time</label>
          <select>
            <option>7:00 AM</option>
            <option>8:00 AM</option>
            <option>9:00 AM</option>
