        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Additional Notes</label>
        <textarea placeholder="Tell us about your vehicle or any special requirements…"></textarea>
      </div>
      <button class="form-submit" onclick="handleSubmit(event)">
        💧 Confirm Booking
